snippet: For the fourth time in the last five weeks, heavily armed kidnappers believed to be from Somalia successfully struck inside Kenya, this time abducting two European aid workers.
lead_paragraph: For the fourth time in the last five weeks, heavily armed kidnappers believed to be from Somalia successfully struck inside Kenya, this time abducting two European aid workers.
